race.comment: DAYTONA SUNSET (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (25.93) last time in a Grade 6 at this track. Rates on top in this line up. REDMAN JOHNNY (1) produced a moderate performance last time when seventh at this track over 457m behind Big Bang (26.00) in a Grade 6. Expected to feature in the finish. BOMB SUE (8) was strong over this course and distance last time despite filling the minors, finishing half a length behind Stormy Mustang in 25.84 and recording a new PB here. Strong run and expected to feature again. MYSTIC ART (7) is a last-start placegetter who will have admirers.
